Optimize Data Extraction by Excluding Rows in Tabular Data

Exclude rows during table extraction that you do not need to save by using the new Skip record option in the Intelligent Form Reader. Gain better control over the extraction process to capture only the relevant information.

Where: This change applies to the Lightning Experience of multiple Industries clouds.
Who: Apart from Financial Services Cloud, Health Cloud, and Public Sector Solutions, Intelligent Form Reader is also available with the Intelligent Form Reader add-on license for the Automotive, Consumer Goods, Education, Manufacturing, Media, and Net Zero clouds.
